===Vowels===
Sa'och contrasts nine vowel qualities which can be either short or long, yielding a total of 18 vowel phonemes. Diphthongs do not occur in native Sa'och words, but the diphthongs {{IPA|/iə/}}, {{IPA|/ɯə/}}, and {{IPA|/uə/}} may be found in loan words from Thai and Khmer. The vowels of Sa'och are:<ref name="adapted from Isara 2009, pg 73"/>

